{"tid":2194402,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔喺Wolipay名單，但播viuTV嘅茶餐廳，係咪算係黃店？","createTime":"2020-09-08T13:02:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-08T14:33:09.000Z","uid":201027,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d1ff832eac320773f0da52a9c08215822c9936b1","tid":2194402,"uid":201027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T13:02:26.000Z","msg":"同一個好大食嘅男仔朋友出去<br />\n諗住幫襯一間黃店，但居然要排兩個鐘！<br />\n佢想飽肚平快靚正，唔想去上樓文青cafe<br />\n就喺附近茶記落腳：<br />\n「嗱，佢地長開ViuTV㗎，聽個老細同啲客講嘅嘢，又反政府嘅，最重要係唔使排隊吖嘛！」<br />\n<br />\n入到去，清一色阿伯，得我地最後生。但果然係開viuTV，老細同客吹水又確係屌政府喎！<br />\n<br />\n呢種餐廳算係淺黃？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bdf361e2d2ec867214392201ef466cb87db7736","tid":2194402,"uid":312363,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T13:06:31.000Z","msg":"乜一定係後生先可以屌政府？"},{"pid":"ae9d25bed1b8a5233c5cdc407dc6dcc7fb3ed472","tid":2194402,"uid":9,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T13:08:14.000Z","msg":"黃店要自己報㗎嘛<br />\n個個都唔報邊到嚟先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n識一間有埋光時旗都冇上架"},{"pid":"5fccf11f441a4267d5a61df1f8c48e35cb988cdd","tid":2194402,"uid":222499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T13:16:24.000Z","msg":"我會睇埋香港人的飲食購物天地FB再cross check"},{"pid":"6fbdac7fa2926dab6bc6a14aa40f1de1ce42f495","tid":2194402,"uid":273014,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T13:17:56.000Z","msg":"有啲黃店會因為唔同原因而選擇低調，例如唔想間店俾人搞、唔想啲人只係因為佢係黃店，而唔係佢哋嘅質素而幫襯。<br />\n<br />\n如果人哋唔想報就唔好幫佢報，但幫襯嘅話，why not?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea10d1782c6bf7dd1002e5d152805402a7f0d345","tid":2194402,"uid":201027,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4bdf361e2d2ec867214392201ef466cb87db7736","tid":2194402,"uid":312363,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T13:06:31.000Z","msg":"乜一定係後生先可以屌政府？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-08T14:33:09.000Z","msg":"唔係，但去黃店排隊嘅多數係後生仔女"}]}